description: Try our easy to follow Squid With Cucumber & Radish Salad recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Squid With Cucumber & Radish Salad Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat 1 tbs oil in a wok over high heat. Add 1/3 of the squid and stir-fry for 2 minutes or until golden and cooked through. Transfer to a plate. Repeat with remaining squid, adding more oil as required. Serve squid with cucumber salad and lime wedges.
